These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, freelancer, dancer
1. the freelancer is on the far left##1
2. the accountant is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | freelancer | dancer | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, designer, pilot
1. the pilot is on the far right##1
2. the videographer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | videographer | designer | pilot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, skydiving, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | camping | skydiving | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
