1. the pakistani is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is on the right of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Nationality   | colombian | american | pakistani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-5::.
