.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, helicopter, trike
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | trike | helicopter | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, time-travel, horror
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | romance | time-travel |

